      "author": "JoaoNoturno",
      "description": "## Initial Release\r\n\r\nReplace Em Dash is a simple and lightweight Obsidian plugin that automatically converts double hyphens (`--`) into an em dash (`—`) while typing.\r\n\r\n### Features\r\n\r\n- Automatically replaces `--` with `—`\r\n- Works in real-time while typing\r\n- Lightweight and minimal\r\n- No configuration required\r\n\r\nThis is the first stable release (v1.0.0).",
